Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ratu Filorial yang sama seperti Filo,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.41,0:00:08.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,dijadikan spesies burung nasional\Ndi Q'ten Lo,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami memulai perjalanan
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.19,0:00:13.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,menuju ibu kota dengan Filo\Ndi barisan depan sesuai saran Raluva.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dampaknya luar biasa,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.53,0:00:20.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami disambut di kota-kota yang kami lewati\Ndalam perjalanan menuju ibu kota lama,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.55,0:00:23.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kami dapat menguasainya\Ntanpa perlawanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.45,0:00:33.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak menyangka dampaknya bisa begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.21,0:00:37.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masalah dampak ini,\Nsama sepertimu, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.37,0:00:39.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.01,0:00:43.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang tidak puas\Ndengan Kaisar Surgawi saat ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.84,0:00:46.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,niscaya akan bergabung dengan pihak kita\Njika melihat pakaian ini
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang merupakan bukti Kaisar Surgawi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.17,0:00:51.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan mungkin akan lebih lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.95,0:00:52.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.61,0:00:58.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkat Nona Raphtalia dan burung ilahi,\Nibu kota lama sudah dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan menunggu\Npasukan berikutnya di kamp ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Butuh waktu dua sampai tiga hari\Nuntuk bisa berkumpul.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.15,0:01:08.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku tidak mau berhenti,\Ntapi apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.18,0:01:11.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah kita merebut ibu kota lama,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.39,0:01:15.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita akan mengadakan upacara untuk\Nmewarisi Kaisar Surgawi di tempat suci.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.71,0:01:16.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.71,0:01:20.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya karena memperoleh\Nkekuatan Kaisar Surgawi,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukan berarti langsung jadi\NKaisar Surgawi yang baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan terlalu dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh, ke sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.01,0:01:45.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm, kudengar menuju ke sini...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm, apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke! Ke sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.35,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Seperti biasa, mereka tidak menyetujui\Ngencatan senjata, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bupati Makina mungkin\Ntidak berniat melakukan hal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.11,0:03:40.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada juga laporan bahwa pasukan pemerintah\Ndipanggil ke ibu kota lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi mereka sepenuhnya siap untuk melawan...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Naga Air,\Nkomandan Pasukan Komando Surgawi,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah memasuki ibu kota lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang macam apa dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangnya aku mengirim\Nmata-mata berkali-kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, tidak ada yang kembali satu pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah keluar dari negeri ini\Naku pun tidak tahu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir seseorang di keluarga itu\Nyang melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalipun kita berhasil\Nsampai ke ibu kota lama,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,pertempuran tidak dapat dihindari.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju terus jangan lengah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tuanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya makan sudah siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan pergi memeriksa bengkel.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian makanlah duluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raphtalia dan Filo ada parade besok,\Njadi tidurlah lebih awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atla dan Fohl akan berlatih\Nsetelah makan malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalipun kau Tuan Naofumi,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.95,0:04:45.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tak bisa membiarkanmu\Nberjalan sendirian di wilayah asing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku menjadi pendampingmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atla, kau itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan Perisai,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisakah mengizinkan mengantar\Nsetidaknya sampai tengah jalan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu aku akan berlatih atau apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fohl, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bilang kalian berdua berlatih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhenti memanjakan Atla.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mengantarmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku tidak diberi arahan,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.31,0:05:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,maka aku yang akan menjaganya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong berjaga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,S'yne, aku mohon, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gara-gara Kakak,\Ntugasku jadi diambil oleh orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atla, aku berusaha untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak, tolong jangan mengatakan\Nhal yang tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu, ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak. Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.68,0:05:55.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku ingin bertanya sesuatu.\NJalan depan sebelah mana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jalan depan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,langsung saja ke gang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, bonekanya bisa bicara!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucunya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, biasa saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau mau ke jalan depan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.55,0:06:13.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, iya juga.\NJalan depan ke sini, 'kan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Anchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tepat waktu sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong katakan padanya\Nuntuk melepas talinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mengatakan ingin meninggalkan\Npekerjaannya dan pergi keluar untuk minum.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita bertemu lagi, ya, Nona.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cantik seperti biasa, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa seperti dibutakan\Noleh kecerahannya matamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masalah pedang itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana pekerjaan perbaikan
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.21,0:06:57.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,pedang terkutuk yang kutitipkan\Npadamu kemarin?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.90,0:07:02.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tingkat kerusakan sebesar itu\Nmudah bagi Muramasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu-satunya peralatan yang dibutuhkan\Nada di bengkel ibu kota lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh iya, Nona!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita cari beberapa alat bersama!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.71,0:07:15.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika denganmu, kita pasti akan\Nmenemukan alat yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong kosong.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, setidaknya soal bengkel\Ndi ibu kota lama itu sepertinya benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,kurasa kita akan menempa ulang pedang itu\Nsetelah kita mengamankan ibu kota lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau, yang tadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tersesat lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namamu siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zodia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zodia?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama yang cantik!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pandai besi terbaik di negara ini,\Ntidak, di dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Muramasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.38,0:07:57.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada toko yang menyajikan alkohol\Nyang luar biasa lezat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah ini mau pergi bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oi, cepat lepaskan talinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetapi aku harus pergi melihat parade orang
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang akan jadi Kaisar Surgawi baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.31,0:08:11.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Parade? Kalau itu sih, besok...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok aku yang akan memandumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk saat ini, silakan datang\Ndan bergabunglah denganku malam ini
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk mempererat persahabatan kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minum alkohol!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau ikut, aku mungkin juga ikut.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku mau pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, S'yne.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangku. Jangan bicara\Nhal kejam seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah itu pedang terkutuk\Natau perlengkapan sayangku,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan terus menempanya sampai aku mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, temanilah dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asyik! Alkohol!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan sebelah sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tutup.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini adalah tempatku menginap.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lantai dua jadi penginapan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, berarti ini adalah takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berisik di depan warung!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat ini tidak ada apa pun di toko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan coba di tempat lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah, aku mohon.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan masuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku juga! permisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oi, kalian, ayo masuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masakan yang luar biasa, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, duh, duh, duh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, untuk pertemuan kita!\NBersulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa malah kau yang memimpin?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuat dengan alkohol, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku juga kuat terhadap alkohol.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum tahu nama Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iwatani Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, Dik Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.94,0:10:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dik?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.20,0:10:22.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dik Naofumi, spesiesnya apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku spesies komai.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia bisa sekuat ini dengan alkohol?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mau kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oi! Ayo kita main permainan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permainan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begini bisa lebih meriah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permainan Tuan Kaisar Surgawi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo main kartu Masuzu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.38,0:10:49.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, kartu Masuzu?\NKalau begitu, ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, aku tidak bilang mau ikut main.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan juga sepertinya\Nbersemangat melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini pertama kali kau memainkannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu permainan yang mirip.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat, hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga minum!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial! Kalah lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Naofumi kuat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo sekali lagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya tidur juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan juga sepertinya mengantuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok harus bangun pagi.\NSaatnya kita pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo sekali lagi saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok kau mau menonton parade, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika bertemu lagi harus main ini lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Janji!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, janji dengan bersulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih minum?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terima ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.30,0:12:05.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini benar-benar menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya aku\Nmerasa senang seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah terlalu mabuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kartu tanda tangan sebagai tanda\Nperayaan pertemuan denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, aku memberikannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau mau jadi suamiku?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau anggap serius, ya?\NIya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa dengan yang mabuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Naofumi, sampai jumpa, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Janji, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sana, masuk ke dalam!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku serius, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terkejut kalian bisa\Nmendapat makanan sebanyak ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.14,0:13:12.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, ini semua berkat Kaisar Surgawi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya apa yang dilakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini, silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak. Ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.64,0:13:28.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, tolong berhenti\Nmemanggil "kakak" seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, tolong mengantre dari sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. jangan memotong antrean.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, Fohl.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, ada yang terjadi tadi malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.91,0:13:44.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya berbicara padanya\Nsedikit soal Atla.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, Kakak ini selalu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang itu demi kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.84,0:13:58.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya, aku tidak bisa\Nikut dengan Tuan Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan lihat apakah bisa keluar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fohl.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, eh, biarkan sajalah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya untuk keluar sebentar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sudah berlatih,\Ndan Atla juga bilang ingin pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika Fohl tidak menghentikannya\Nlalu akan bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika memang kau benar-benar memikirkan Atla,\Naku tidak akan bicara apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Fohl yang sekarang...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya bisa melihatmu\Nsedang memanjakan Atla.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika keadaan terus berlanjut seperti ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,suatu hari nanti hal ini mungkin\Nmenjadi tidak dapat diubah lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika memang memikirkan kebahagiaan Atla...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.94,0:14:51.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku ada saatnya harus\Nbertengkar dan menghentikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fohl sebagai seorang kakak...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah harus melindunginya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Kakak?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus melakukan hal yang benar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.95,0:15:11.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin menjadi kakak\Nyang hebat seperti Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tolong mengantre dari sini!\N- Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok kita akhirnya akan\Nmemasuki ibu kota lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Naofumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga masuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu! Jangan masuk! Jangan masuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.99,0:16:20.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar, kau pasti tersesat lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah kau melihat paradenya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku juga melihat Kaisar Surgawi\Nyang baru. Naofumi juga lihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kalau itu sih, iya...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, menurutmu Kaisar Surgawi baru\Norangnya bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang seperti apa...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau begitu penasaran\Ndengan Kaisar Surgawi baru?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku Kaisar Surgawi\Nyang sekarang bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.77,0:16:48.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kondisi Q'ten Lo sedang tidak baik-baik saja\Ndan semua orang kesusahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, pemerintahan yang buruk itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaanku juga makin berat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan yang tidak bersih?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan kotor?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu semua harus aku lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan kotor?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pikir itu berat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku ingin semuanya tertawa,\Ntapi tidak berjalan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.94,0:17:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, datang ke sini, aku melihat\Nsemua orang tertawa setelah sekian lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.11,0:17:23.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tengah senyuman itu,\Nada Kaisar Surgawi baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.80,0:17:30.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melihat itu, aku merasa jadi tahu\Nbagaimana cara membuat semua tersenyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.38,0:17:34.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, aku berpikir ingin berbicara\Ndengan Kaisar Surgawi baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya, tiba-tiba berbicara begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh iya, ayo bermain kartu Masuzu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah janji jika bertemu lagi mau main.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ayo ke penginapan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makin banyak orang akan menarik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asyik!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mari kita minum untuk\Nmenghibur diri sebelum pertandingan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku meninggalkannya\Ndi pemandian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan cek di pemandian pria,\Ntunggulah di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang untung menjemput.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada! Ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.85,0:18:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menjadi Pendeta Naga Air itu\Nmemang tugas yang berat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu adalah pekerjaan\Nmelayani Kaisar Surgawi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Naga Air mungkin\Nmemiliki nama yang megah,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.57,0:18:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,tetapi tugasnya termasuk\Nmemimpin pasukan ke medan perang
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan melaksanakan hukuman mati yang diberikan\Nkepada penjahat oleh Kaisar Surgawi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eksekusi penjahat...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun kita menyebutnya "penjahat",
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.11,0:19:05.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,semua orang yang tidak sesuai\Ndengan kehendak Kaisar Surgawi
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah orang berdosa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan kotor, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang juga, salah satu dari anggota\Nkeluargaku sepertinya melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tidak ada harapan bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.21,0:19:23.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang kau bilang waktu itu,\Nsoal keluargamu itu siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.01,0:19:28.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama beberapa generasi, spesies kami\Ntelah dipilih karena kemampuan bertarungnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juga dikenal sebagai pendeta pembantai.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta pembantai...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seram, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.51,0:19:40.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini sebenarnya mengerikan, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa berbuat apa-apa\Nkarena posisi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.61,0:19:49.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tetap harus diselesaikan\Ndi suatu tempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua tumben, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang dihibur Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok sampai ke ibu kota lama,\Nmari kita tidur lebih awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lapor!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada malam hari, di kota belakang
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,dilaporkan disergap oleh apa\Nyang tampak seperti pasukan pemerintah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,DI kota belakang harusnya\Nada Rishia dan Itsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atla, Fohl, S'yne!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa pergi dengan Gaelion untuk membantu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dimengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.80,0:21:01.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan melaporkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebuah surat telah tiba dari seseorang\Nyang mengaku sebagai utusan musuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Utusan musuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepada: Komandan Pemberontak.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertanda...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Naga Air...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Naga Air?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Isinya apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong bacakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.78,0:21:18.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada aksi militer prematur tadi malam,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,tetapi ini bukan niatku sebagai\Nkomandan pasukan pemerintah,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.85,0:21:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan sekarang berada di bawah kendaliku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam pertempuran ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami berharap perwakilan kedua belah pihak
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan bertemu langsung\Ndan melakukan negosiasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentara kami diwakili olehku,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.53,0:21:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tentaramu diwakili oleh\Nseorang komandan atau yang setara.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.14,0:21:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terasa sepihak sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.21,0:21:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia cukup baik untuk\Nseorang dari keluargaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku melihat suratnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
